and being in that culture,\\\" the customer said.\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A little further east in Kansas City, Missouri, those looking to cool off with a French treat can swing by French Custard in the Brookside neighborhood.\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kansas_City_metropolitan_area\", \"score\": 0.999999999984766, \"rank\": 9.408496329160594e-12, \"text\": \"Kansas City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kansas_City_metropolitan_area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kansas_City_metropolitan_area\"}, {\"begin\": 1588, \"end\": 1596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missouri\", \"score\": 0.8786964716795228, \"rank\": 0.13804558612085352, \"text\": \"Missouri\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missouri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missouri\"}, {\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998562902625632, \"rank\": 0.0001368082063184235, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1657, \"end\": 1663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998562902625632, \"rank\": 0.0001368082063184235, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Custard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.428659712539052e-20, \"text\": \"Custard\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Custard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Custard\"}, {\"begin\": 1679, \"end\": 1688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brookside_High_School\", \"score\": 0.991567009603995, \"rank\": 0.008495009339670873, \"text\": \"Brookside\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brookside_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brookside_High_School\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We really tried to do things the French way, which is simple but delicious and homemade and high quality,\\\"French Custardowner Jessica Wood said.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1831, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Buchanan\", \"score\": 0.8323062559553221, \"rank\": 0.1352934525252756, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Buchanan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I definitely feel like we will have a boost in sales this summer with people wanting to just try French custard.\\\"\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998562902625632, \"rank\": 0.0001368082063184235, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wood, who has visited France and lived in New York, saw a need to bring authentic French custard to Kansas City by opening up her shop in 2023.\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1988, \"end\": 1994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9796042122722536, \"rank\": 0.020748987657799704, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2008, \"end\": 2016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\",